{"id":463250,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":2,"day":2}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"迎春诗会","genre":"","count":"124","ytitle":"","mtitle":"海滨新村","ftitle":"","authors":["毛炳甫"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"华东电力建设局　上海工程处　毛炳甫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"柳下卧着黄浦江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开门就见三尺浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白帆点点镜中移，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明涛声叩门窗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新壁高挂领袖像，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家升起红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里想起毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千家万户光方丈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这儿人们多豪爽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心话写在门板上:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“永远听毛主席话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决跟着共产党。”"}]}